des:
Guests may order pizza and sides from Pizza Paradise and apply specials to cart before "purchase." Guests may also get information such as specials, locations, sizes, toppings, and sides available at Pizza Paradise.

Note: Pizza Paradise is a fictional company, and customer and payment information are not collected.
